
Canvas controls
---------------------
LCLICK+DRAG		Draw with foreground color
RCLICK+DRAG		Draw with background color
MCLICK+DRAG		Draw with tertiary color
SHIFT+CLICK+DRAG	Select if first trixel not already selected, deselect otherwise
ALT+LCLICK		Set foreground color
ALT+RCLICK		Set background color
ALT+MCLICK		Set tertiary color
C			Copy selection
X			Cut selection, replacing with background color
V			Reduplicate the previously copied section

Copying controls
---------------------
UP/DOWN/LEFT/RIGHT	Move the copied section
COMMA/PERIOD		Rotate the copied section left/right
C/V			Paste

Color Controls
---------------------
LCLICK (on actives)	Set that color with HVS
SPACE			Cycle foreground, background, and tertiary colors
LCLICK (on palette)	Switch foreground color to that palette color
ALT+LCLICK		Set palette color
1-0			Switch the foreground color to corresponding palette color
